_aChangeLog.text: Moved two bombsites to the towers as requested by user, tested them out and they work good.

_aLatestUpdates._sText: Also adjusted lightning in parking house.

_sText:
Hello folks,

This here is a new map I have worked on, which took hours upon hours to make.
It is a traditional DE-map (bomb/defuse-map).
Although it has a twist with three sites (A-red, A-white and a B-site).

I do not have a minimap/radar for this though but I hope you will enjoy it anyways.
